n semi-solid, N-free media.</s><s>Variable with respect to use of nitrate and perchlorate as terminal electron acceptors.</s><s>Heterotrophic.</s><s>Oxidase-positive.</s><s>Catalase-positive.</s><s>Capable of nitrogen fixation.</s><s>Growth does not occur on most amino acids, nor on mono-or disaccharides.</s><s>Optimum growth temperature about 37 °C.</s><s>Produces polyhydroxybutyrate storage granules.</s><s>Neutral pH optimal for growth.</s><s>Major cellular fatty acids are C<sub>16 : 1</sub><em>ω</em>7c, C<sub>16 : 0</sub> and C<sub>18 : 1</sub><em>ω</em>7c.</s><s>G+C content of DNA is 65–68 mol%.</s><s>Type species is <em>Azospira oryzae</em>.</s></p></content></protolog>